    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227470/extras/b44832dce643993fa9fc52870edd088c.poster.avif?t=1761843635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227470/extras/b44832dce643993fa9fc52870edd088c.webm?t=1761843635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;The Eldritch Ascent&quot; Is a new grimdark fantasy narrative driven turn based game. Explore and battle your way up the twisted spire as the Eldritch, a wretched lost soul brought back from the depths by a mysterious demon. Play the demo now available to download.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227470/extras/3f0b93888f8d63b8fbaf8906fe3b81aa.poster.avif?t=1761843635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227470/extras/3f0b93888f8d63b8fbaf8906fe3b81aa.webm?t=1761843635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227470/extras/6693c53a0bd39bf023318456142df38e.poster.avif?t=1761843635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227470/extras/6693c53a0bd39bf023318456142df38e.webm?t=1761843635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ascend The Tower -</i> Fight your way through the mysterious Tower of Trials, where each floor brings tougher enemies and greater challenges. Face hordes of enemies as you climb, building your strength and strategy to reach the top!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Unlock Powerful Skills</i>: Choose skills wisely to create your own fighting style and adapt to the ever-changing threats within the tower. Challenge powerful boss enemies at key levels, each with their own unique moves and patterns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Unravel The Story: </i>Uncover a gripping narrative as you progress, with story elements unfolding on each floor. Meet allies, encounter rivals, and piece together the history of the tower as you climb towards its peak.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227470/extras/42c232d0d28bb3984aece72528cc91b2.webp?t=1761843635\" width=618 height=39 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Amidst the creeping shadows of the insidious tower, despair is not an escape but a promise fulfilled.&quot;</i></p></li></ul>",
